<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/28988380">怎样把《乡村爱情》写出《冰与火之歌》的感觉？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3778279" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">象牙山四大家族的恩怨情仇</div>


