<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$DKyisi" href="/people/DKyisi">邓璋</a>，<strong title="学生" class="zu-question-my-bio">学生</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="54">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$marigram" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/marigram" class="zg-link" title="Marigram">Marigram</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ni-hao-32-5" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ni-hao-32-5" class="zg-link" title="無驮">無驮</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3778279" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">我吱一声：虽然广坤和泰温差太多，不过我真心觉得谢永强很像詹姆啊。。。<br><br>1.农村大学生（高学历） VS 最年轻的御林铁卫——年少有成；<br>2.不听爹的话办果园 VS 不听爹的话当国王护卫——叛父情节；<br>3.心地都很善良，当然也都有点懦弱；<br>4.长得都挺帅；<br>5.所有台词可以总结为两句：爹你这是干啥呢/爹我去趟果园 VS 爹你这是干啥呢/爹我不回凯岩城
<a href="/question/28988380/answer/45082859" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
